    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for those who prioritize function over aesthetics. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the car shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the roof and minor wear on the driver's seat. You should expect some typical older-car maintenance needs, such as minor fluid seeps and a suspension that is no longer as firm as it once was. It is a solid, honest car that will get you where you need to go without any hidden surprises.",
