      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in a state of pristine refinement, showcasing an immaculate exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original showroom luster. Meticulously maintained and mechanically flawless, it represents the pinnacle of its class for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than absolute excellence. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly peerless condition.",
